cdata.name: 1World
cdata.desc:
1Worls is a digital-data collecting platform. Its objective is to provide users (brands) with the tools for customer behavior studies and opinions.To understand thepublic needs and wills, users are able toperform Polls,Quizzes, Surveys, and Trivia activities at the 1World platform, also it has aCompare & Contrast system so the user can analyze the Before vs After effect.

The 1WO token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency. It is the medium for all payments processedat the 1Worlds platform and allows end users (readers) on the siteto earn tokens by collecting points for engagements and contributionswithin the brands' campaigns.
